title: Star Wars BAD BATCH 1x14: Every EASTER EGG + Anakin Skywalker CLONE Explained | Full BREAKDOWN
author: ScreenCrush
comment: Who do you think Omega is a clone of?
Forgot the Small Easter Egg nod to Republic Commando, The silver and Yellow Commando RC-1262 who Is Scorch. A Very nice little touch to a game that isnt considered cannon anymore.
When Hunter took his fall through the forest, it was straight out of the movie Rambo, First Blood. Interesting that his look is also a tribute to Rambo.
If they got scorch in there they better get the rest of delta squad
description:
Star Wars the Bad Batch rockets to its finale with Hunter now in the clutches of Crosshair and the Empire. This episode has numerous Easter Eggs and lays the groundwork for Rise of Skywalker and the Mandalorian. The episode draws most heavily from A New Hope, and finally transitions the Imperial military away from the Clone Wars and into the era of the rebellion.
